name: USA names for 1880's births
explanation: Top 1000 names based on Social Security card applications for births that occurred in the United States. First names are from births in the 1880's. Last names are based on 1850 US census data.
structure: The fist name table also stores the gender variable which is displayed in the resultPattern.
note: The name tables have been sorted from the most common to the least common.
to do: Chronologically closer first and last name data would be nice.
